data.description: Lovely home nestled in a gated community near Kirtland AFB and plenty of shopping and restaurants.  This two-story home boasts two owner's suites, one downstairs and one upstairs.  Upstairs also houses the laundry. for convenience. This is such a spacious home, it is surprising!  Please come take a look and you will  not be disappointed!   The  stepsaving kitchen has the dining nook nearby and opens to the living room and out onto the open patio area.  The corner lot makes the outdoor space much larger than many of the surrounding homes.  Located nearby is the community park for outdoor fun!
